Package remodel.util

The standard library used by compiled ReMoDeL components.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Anthony J H Simons
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Function<T,​S>
    Function is the interface satisfied by dynamically created classes that implement the S apply(T) method.
    Predicate<T>
    Predicate is the interface satisfied by dynamically created classes that implement the boolean apply(T) method.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PureCollection<T>
    PureCollection is the abstract ancestor of constructive collections.
    PureList<T>
    PureList is the ReMoDeL constructive list type.
    PureSet<T>
    PureSet is the ReMoDeL constructive set type.
    Top
    Top is a default abstract root class for generated Java classes.
    TopRule
    TopRule is an abstract ancestor for generated Java transformation classes.
